rows.label: qev065403_MSG0001
rows.name:
I have some friends on that advance team.
Please, you've got to help them.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065403_MSG0002
rows.name:
And try to keep this on the quiet side, yeah?
We don't want to cause a panic here in the city.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065403_MSG0003
rows.name:
It's best if it's just a small team that heads to the north
fortress.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065403_MSG0004
rows.name: Oh, are you the BLADE Lara hired to help?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065403_MSG0005
rows.name:
...Whoa, hold on! I'm the real Clemons,
not the Definian with the bum intel![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065403_MSG0006
rows.name: I didn't even realize I'd been impersonated.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065403_MSG0007
rows.name:
I was out of the city on a mission. I get back,
and all of a sudden I'm in some weird nightmare.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065403_MSG0008
rows.name:
And now that thing's impersonating Suriella!
Well, I haven't seen her around here, so maybe you
should try searching a different area.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065403_MSG0010
rows.name:
I just heard somebody say they saw a body in the
industrial district.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065403_MSG0011
rows.name: Could be related to this case.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065403_MSG0012
rows.name:
Lara said he was on his way there now.
Maybe it's worth meeting up with him?[ST:wait ]
